ic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328650/extras_big/e3370a270958c99f4cfa13261d9e4b50.avif?t=1759310052 width=800 height=58 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328650/extras/7fcc637be3bb4bcf1143bbb44a6ff0e8.poster.avif?t=1759310052\" width=720 height=255 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2328650/extras/7fcc637be3bb4bcf1143bbb44a6ff0e8.webm?t=1759310052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your train to travel to new places, explore them, and meet some quirky inhabitants. Get to know them, help them with their problems, and progress through the game's main story to save your hometown Barrenpyre from its dire environmental struggles. </p>",
